Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.26,0:01:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.05,0:01:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨Wagnaria
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.22,0:01:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問您一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是來面試打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.23,0:01:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是來面試的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫東田
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這就去請示店長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能麻煩您稍等一會兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.66,0:02:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服務態度很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這家店感覺不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.76,0:02:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不想工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:30.52,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(330,920)\fade(255,0,255,9,551,4471,5014)\be1}「打工改變人生」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.43,0:02:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.16,0:02:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是店長 榊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東田大輔 高一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧 這所也算是重點高中了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 算是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學習很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還行不過我挺喜歡學習的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.01,0:02:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.43,0:03:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 為什麼想到要打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 理由隨意點也沒關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為父親的公司破產了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好沉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 再來一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.83,0:03:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸的公司破產啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:25.50,Notes,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}註:「爸爸」和「破產」兩詞發音類似
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好蹩腳的笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破…破產了？爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 破產那也是沒辦法的事呢 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊爸爸 不要輸給破產
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸他…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破產…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是同音詞的笑話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.99,0:03:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 別生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:03:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉職的公司已經定下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:03:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收入減少了 這話先放前頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是 下個月開始你就沒零花錢和話費了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被裁員了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 打工什麼的學校肯定不允許
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 你真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了支撐家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主動說要去打工是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸打電話過來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是我批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果零花錢 話費 甚至車費都不給了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不搭車的話離學校有15公里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都得騎單車過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實 這樣成績肯定是要下降的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想打工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這兒近 我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:05:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦 你被錄用了 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那從今天開始好好幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位是大堂經理宮越
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是一個學校的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.77,0:05:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作方面的問題可以請教她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.57,0:05:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面試時候見過的那位嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先教你怎樣揍店長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙弱點在下巴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宮越同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有客人進來後要說「歡迎光臨」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聲音大一些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人走的時候 要說「謝謝惠顧」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人走後 馬上收拾餐具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後揍店長下巴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別在店附近餵小貓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之新人做好這些就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有不懂的來問我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:46.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後那個步驟也必須做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個月不學精的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是那個下場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會小心的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那去大堂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這種人會當服務員
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼鬼 連表情都變了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但為什麼宮越要對店長動粗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.97,0:06:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 發票嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店裡養貓確實不對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泥波波足球少年團大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少體團的「團」字怎麼寫？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,團？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是重點高中的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好聰明啊 東田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這人難不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但總不至於…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,8乘7是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是我想多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,59
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:07:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連科技文明都帶不動你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來去裡面幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是從今天起開始在這兒打工的東田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村主沙友里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.91,0:07:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問您一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:28.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.54,0:07:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是菜單
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請點菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,濃度和往常一樣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.18,0:07:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村…村主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…客人…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位爺爺是這裡的常客
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.19,0:08:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡裡要是加奶的話 他會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要記住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村主很正常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實在要說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是開空調啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她忙著考大學請假的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.05,0:08:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店裡就莫名得又冷又暗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛生間裡還會出現「把村主交出來」的血書
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒有什麼令人很毛骨悚然的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒不如說你那神經粗得讓人驚呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 村主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好 高中生同學聊得挺開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 是東田他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 在說村主的靈感很厲害之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:53.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不相信會有幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟沒有見到過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店長也好 店員也…罷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丫有意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.27,0:09:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是東田 今天新進的兼職生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位是近藤妃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.77,0:09:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.69,0:09:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 妃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多到換班的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個 妃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懶？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果客人看到有這種毫無幹勁的員工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對餐廳的看法也會變差
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以為了餐廳著想 我在這休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.26,0:09:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼展開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你差不多適可而止了 妃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是偷懶 又是抽煙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想不想幹活了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宮越
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:09:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大化改新的時間是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.65,0:10:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己考了個好大學就開始愚弄別人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 妃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像宮越所說 稍微正經點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.87,0:10:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說東田是重點高中是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 算是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,江戶時代中期
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德川吉宗下令學習荷蘭語的兩位學者是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野呂元丈和青木昆陽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也算是拿著時薪的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去幹活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東田帥呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在窗口端走做好的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡的話是大堂服務員負責的 用那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是負責廚房的足立
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫河野 請多關照 新人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.83,0:11:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫東田 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,河野 做個巴菲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡由大堂負責
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜品是廚房負貴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般的店鋪的話 大堂也負責做巴菲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們店比較特殊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特殊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.93,0:11:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,河野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 沒什麼 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你第一天上班就不要接待顧客了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學學其他人怎麼接待…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個咖啡比之前的要淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那傻笑個什麼勁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿出點誠意行不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.96,0:11:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鎌倉 你給我過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鎌倉 你把客人當成什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚民
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志保惹宮越生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:02.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別秀錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 鎌倉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要小看我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點怎麼夠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 我真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從各種意義上說這裡臥虎藏龍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是社長千金
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.29,0:12:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫東田是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫進藤祐太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從店長那裡聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也挺不容易的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是因為各種原因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在做派送報紙 便利店員 這裡 還有牛郎的兼職
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我父親借了錢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從她爸爸那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我勒個去？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.98,0:12:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那這些夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妃！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進藤也是不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那晚上的話比起這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛郎不是更賺錢麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是哦 在這兒的兼職是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.46,0:13:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進藤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 保質期到今天的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有展會結束賣剩的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實本來是不能給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正扔了也是可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.47,0:13:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為現金都被討債的拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借錢是因為自家的店鋪什麼的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精肉店 因為不知道什麼時候會倒閉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就拍了一張照片而隨身帶著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,招牌有問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,招牌問題大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 對肉店來說某種意義上還挺搭的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉？什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小的在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向消費者金融公司借了錢的人的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和貸款方的大小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:13:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進藤 進藤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼連鎌倉也跑過來做兼職
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是個大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那是因為我小時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候甩了志保吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 這怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.95,0:14:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家店 認真工作的只有廚子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 大輔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兼職忙得過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能硬著頭皮來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸也不能認輸啊 找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸真是的 不是工作都已經定下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸糊塗了犯糊塗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.11,0:14:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人終於少了點了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:15:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東田你真是努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不習慣的話會很累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 比起跟那群神經大條的人折騰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是專注工作比較輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神經大條？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.29,0:15:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 大輔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太羞恥了 你們趕緊回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是要撒謊 也要說現在正忙之類的吧 大輔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說我家哪來的錢可以在外面買著吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種程度的話還是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是就是 哥哥你太擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊回…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是東田的家人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.03,0:15:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直承蒙照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.66,0:15:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 大輔才受你們關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漢堡肉牛排是嗎 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:15:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請稍等片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 東田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你復活了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家人有沒有說些奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會當作沒聽見的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店員結賬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大輔 雖然在家裡面我們是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡可是客人和店員的關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請好好分清楚認真工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.00,0:16:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾也是能說些正經話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝惠顧 總共8280日元
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大輔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸我忘了帶錢了幫我付下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:16:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說好的分清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.19,0:17:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東田完全適應工作了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼說也打了半個月的工了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經二月了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到二月 東田 就是情人節吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.79,0:17:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是聖瓦倫丁的忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吃我做的巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用 別同情我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 東田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和人情 本命啥的沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之請吃我做的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說好了哦 來拉鈎上吊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宮越 你到底想給我做什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.78,0:17:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東田是今年的擔當呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.99,0:17:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃宮越巧克力的擔當
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擔當？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年果斷就讓東田上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猜拳輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下 村主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果吃了宮越的巧克力會怎麼樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 一定要舉個例子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.10,0:18:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好比聖瓦倫丁大人降臨在眼前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…的味道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.07,0:18:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瀕死體驗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於到14號了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次過這麼緊張的情人節
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 能收下嗎 東田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊啊 最後還是收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.27,0:19:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進藤真是受歡迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 祐太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.65,0:19:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就直接帶過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是男公關俱樂部的客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.82,0:19:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真開心 今天也好多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣暫時還能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情人節快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我給你的禮物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…那是…錢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個錢現在去商場買巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選一個最貴的去收銀說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「這是本命巧克力 請幫我包裝的漂亮點」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後買完後 剩下的找零就給你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找零…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要的話 巧克力也給你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.86,0:19:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 宮越…巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃掉 不准扔掉 絕對吃掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:20:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有別的想送給的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本命什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不用給我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給本命送巧克力的話 會吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定啊 宮越那麼可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果閉著嘴的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我喜歡你東田
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 宮越
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快點吃吃看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來倒是很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的啦 應該
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.91,0:20:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就吃一個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.82,0:21:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.53,0:21:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.53,0:21:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Love and Peace哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.87,0:21:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖…瓦倫丁大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.96,0:21:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還叫我名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 東田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去把這個丟掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.09,0:21:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…宮越
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得你…努力做的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.64,0:21:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為Love and peace 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…會把它帶回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.94,0:21:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東 東田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者啊 勇者東田
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.24,0:23:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是我開始打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大輔 這個可以吃掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.98,0:23:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是有這種打算才帶回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.91,0:23:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一話也讓人很期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.50,0:23:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 但是比起對話的腦洞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.91,0:23:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也請大家經緊跟季節的腦洞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.21,0:23:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一話「人生沒有那麼簡單」
